quran[14{c,v,t}:
106,1,Li-ilaafi quraish
106,2,Elaafihim rihlatash shitaa-i wass saif
106,3,Fal y'abudu rabba haazal-bait
106,4,Allazi at'amahum min ju'inw-wa-aamana hum min khawf
107,1,Ara-aital lazee yu kazzibu bid deen
107,2,Fa zaalikal lazi yadu'ul-yateem
107,3,Wa la ya huddu 'alaa ta'amil miskeen
107,4,Fa wai lul-lil mu salleen
107,5,Al lazeena hum 'an salaatihim sahoon
107,6,Al lazeena hum yuraa-oon
107,7,Wa yamna'oonal ma'oon
108,1,Innaa a'taina kal kauthar
108,2,Fa salli li rabbika wanhar
108,3,Inna shani-aka huwal abtar
